title: Mike Arnoldi's Annual Birthday Party & Concert
desc: As you may know every year I throw my Birthday Party & Concert to benefit a Children's Hospital Charity.? This year is gonna be the biggest show ever in mean of the band.? BUT it will be very private.? Only 200 people can attend but band we have sells out all their venues they play in.? I am putting up tickets to this December 5th event now for 2 reasons.? One cause it will fill up fast, but 2 we are going to need funds in advance for our Children's Hospital project this year early.? We are sending a Santa to the hospital to ask the kids what they want them we are going to get these items.? May their chistmas gift wish come true.? Tickets are just $20 each.? The person hosting is an Oscar Nominated alister.? Don't delay order now.
